if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('busi_noticereply')
and type = 'U')
drop table busi_noticereply
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_noticereply */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_noticereply (
ReplyID int identity,
NoticeID int not null,
Content varchar(3000) not null,
AppTime datetime not null default getdate(),
IsDel bit not null default 0,
constraint PK_BUSI_NOTICEREPLY primary key (ReplyID)
)
go

if exists (select 1 from sys.extended_properties
where major_id = object_id('busi_noticereply') and minor_id = 0)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_noticereply'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'业务-公告回复表',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_noticereply'
go
